  <aspecttable>SE TSFS 2010</aspecttable>
  <name>Single three aspect distant signal</name>
  <reference>See wikipedia <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swedish_railway_signalling">Swedish railway signaling</a>
  for english information.</reference>
  <description>Single distant signal to indicate what next main signal is showing.
  No points or main dwarf signal allowed between single distance signal and next main signal.</description>

